{"tid":264551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國首測攔截洲際彈道導彈　國防部稱成功及具阻嚇力","createTime":"2017-05-31T02:19:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T04:44:18.000Z","uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"96959dd60af289dafda8e2b599e2b32f46dfcae4","tid":264551,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T02:19:56.000Z","msg":"美國首測攔截洲際彈道導彈　國防部稱成功及具阻嚇力<br />\n<br />\n美國首次測試攔截洲際彈道導彈，國防部宣布測試成功。美軍在聲明說，從加州空軍基地發射的攔截飛彈，成功攔截一枚從北太平洋馬紹爾群島美軍導彈試射場發射，模擬越過太平洋攻擊美國的導彈。<br />\n<br />\n五角大樓官員說，攔截系統在防衛美國本土方面，十分重要，今次測試顯示美國應對真實威脅的措施，具有阻嚇力及可以信賴。<br />\n<br />\n不過有報道說，今次測試未能確定，美軍是否有能力在戰爭情況下，攔截北韓以美國為目標的洲際彈道導彈。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1333271-20170531.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1333271-20170531.htm&d=oMvO6dARAbVNNYonBr5xoP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=a8289da0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1333271-20170531.htm&h=8d56952e\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1333271-20170531.htm</a>"},{"pid":"29543a9ca69b8c32873d9b07dc14e8bf80042f41","tid":264551,"uid":112622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T02:24:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c88946041336fdabc076b5ef1ddb16fccd5d37ae","tid":264551,"uid":41974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T02:25:38.000Z","msg":"外星科技"},{"pid":"96d2542222fca33dd4e5b66a3c5c73cf197871b1","tid":264551,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T04:42:11.000Z","msg":"東風molamola"},{"pid":"7eff376f53def9238097c6614b80b93c9a3218b1","tid":264551,"uid":57633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T04:44:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美國嘅攔截導彈可唔可以攔截到自己嘅洲際導彈？🤔</blockquote><br />\n成功攔截一枚從北太平洋馬紹爾群島美軍導彈試射場發射<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n...."}]}